channel.title: Euthymia[DELTA]-DEM ENTITY BASED CB EMULATOR-DEM BOATS-DEM CANOES
channel.description:
Well since im already gonna work on oblivion and also with skyro with something else, i decided i will no longer have time to continue this as euthymia, yet it will be the base for oblivion.
What makes Euthymia better than any other delta or atleast the 95% of delta’s out there? Answers: Euthymia server runs on a Cycle based task manager wich gives flexibility for timers and such. The process and the packets aren’t all cluttered with timers, and redundant code. It doesn’t have a Cryption class that was property of jagex, it uses the Isaaccipher instead. It has a shutdownHook, wich saves the player in case the virtual machine crashes. Most of the code that was made from scratch is commented. It is packaged. The code is almost formatted. Euthymia has object definitions Euthymia has a pathfinder so you wont noclip. And the list could keep going but whatever.
Well i guess i dont have much to say here is the development thread for info i might miss forwards [url=https://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,647772.0.html]Dev thread[/url]
So here is most likely what it has. [code]march-Started project added objecthandler packaged added control panel added a path!finder added a door handler, it opens all the doors in a switch statement on a random direction lawl. Started with client.java 600kb Ripped smelting from an old server i had. ripped some spawns packaged packets are handled on their own file added music added day night system ghost spawn in draynor manor when night. added sounds to most of the actions that can be done. added bone burying added bone on altar Client.java heavely reduced, its like 90kb, yet player java gained like 50kb. Added firemaking Ripped woodcutting Ripped herblore Added fillables removed dropping, and picking up global items. added cow milking added pickables re-did some of the package added flour making added dorics quest added cook assistant added pick pocketing added somewhat lockpicking added thieving stalls added cooking added mining Implementing Entity system.. Entity has had two children! wich are their subclasses Player, and NPC Added canoe.. Added crafting leather.. added smithing interface added smithing for all daggers added smithing for all swords started ripping entity combat system. - Too many changes needed aborted. added crafting for body added crafting for chaps added tanning. added crafting vor coif added crafting for vambraces added crafting for gloves added crafting for boots added smithing for all longswords added smithing for all scimitar added smithing for all 2 handed added music to alot of zones. fixed trading added boat travelling started making combat simulator added sounds and reattacking to the combat simulator le shutdown hook Isaaccipher added right click ban for admins + [/code] Please have in mind that everything mentioned above is in high scale, as there might be lots of things that i dont remember but thats the most important.

EDIT: CHEAPHAX#2: pausing the combat…

[code=java] /*
* Pauses the combat for x ticks.
* @ticks, the number of cycles till the combat will be restarted.
* 1 cycle = 600ms
*/
private static void pauseCombat(final Entity attacker, final Entity victim, final int ticks) {
stopCombat(attacker);
Server.getTaskScheduler().schedule(new Task(2, true) {
private int count = ticks;

		@Override
		protected void execute() {

			if (count > 0) {
				PlayerHandler.messageToAll = count + "...";
				count--;
			} else {
				attack(attacker, victim);
			}
		}
	});
}[/code]bump
